<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en-US"
      lang="en-US"
      metal:use-macro="here/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="passwordresettool">

<tal:comment tal:replace="nothing">
This template based on version from Plone 4.1a3

Rhaptos notes:
  Reformatted text to be more readable. Used to be a P and a BR, but this (3 BRs) is less damaging to the diff)
</tal:comment>

<body>

<metal:main fill-slot="main">

    <h1 class="documentFirstHeading" 
        i18n:translate="heading_sent_password">Password reset confirmation sent</h1>

    <div class="documentDescription" i18n:translate="description_sent_password">
        Your password reset request has been mailed.<br />It should arrive in your
        mailbox momentarily.<br /><br />When you receive the message, visit the address it
        contains to reset your password.
    </div>

</metal:main>

</body>
</html>
